description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Core Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow vibe.
The The Zen Flow vibe means Grounding, intentional, breath-centered, unhurried. This is especially good for When you need balance, mindfulness, and release..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Build strength and stamina in your core with Pete as you work on different variations of planks and Russian twists. ...
